{"tid":2452741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年管有士巴拿及索帶 羅德泉判處被告入勞教中心","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T14:58:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fac1967d42e8c0fdb3d67904b25ff5805bda8cef","tid":2452741,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14508&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2b2e2ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14508</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤胡(19) #1201旺角 <br />\n🛑已還押21日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有適合作非法用途的工具或攻擊性武器並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n被告被控於2019年12月1日，在旺角新填地街近山東街交界，管有一支士巴拿及100條索帶。#管有工具作非法用途<br />\n==============<br />\n法庭判處被告🛑勞教中心🛑"},{"pid":"30404e493e09a0e4f4ca5d2d61857fdc07e455bf","tid":2452741,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d512689b9a376c7971e5a7c88ae7291eb944838","tid":2452741,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7f9b1936427305ce223f1284c5bf3d8bdfd4eb","tid":2452741,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"本身呢單唔係崔美霞判咩？"},{"pid":"d5bebe34785dd2dac8da92b9e751c1b542610034","tid":2452741,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"即場屌個官老母博判監算<br />\n去勞改慘過坐監"},{"pid":"a972f5338